Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.69,0:00:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可能是屬於犯人的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.74,0:00:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是慶賀你工作的禮物	.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.62,0:00:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然話是如此	.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.33,0:00:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經是我用盡我刑警工作的全部工資了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.88,0:00:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.33,0:00:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會   我很高興   謝謝你   前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.47,0:00:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.10,0:01:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.64,0:01:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您當作沒看見吧    課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.52,0:01:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.94,0:01:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泉水先生    現在已經是中午了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下午不是要去大學嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我起來  泉水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是已經醒來的話   就給我趕緊的.......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這不僅僅是一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,唉   所以呢   在這個時代呢.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看昨天的電視劇了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了看了   真奈美醬真的好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這貨在胡說些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.42,0:03:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的是接待員好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴木   我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.61,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你......曾經說過喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是   我還不曾.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼   為什麼不讓我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓我有機會對你說喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就獨自離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.88,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底為什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,cut!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ok 了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.78,0:04:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來   拍攝已經全部結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種季節拍冬季物語真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍馬先生   辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.38,0:05:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  聖夜先生   真是萬分感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是2個小時SP的演員陣容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽您這麼說我的辛苦也是值得的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.22,0:05:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說   我真的沒想到您竟然會接下這份工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.14,0:05:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個    其實我也是有私心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有私心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟龍馬君做對手戲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的演技不錯啊    龍馬君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我佩服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分感謝    聖夜先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.58,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來    這次的外景拍攝感覺你拿出真本事來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是戀愛的演技不錯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太溫柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近是不是遇到什麼好事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒?   好事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍馬   我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.89,0:05:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個.......好像是有又好像沒有又好像有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.73,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦    難道人氣巨星一條龍馬正陷入熱戀中！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.44,0:06:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是賣給狗仔隊的話  一定能賣到一個好價錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導   導演請   您不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.57,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像龍馬君這樣的演員總會有一兩次戀愛經驗的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.11,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說    讓你拍這兩周的海外拍攝    真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我向你老婆道歉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.66,0:06:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆是......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你放過我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖夜先生    我已經把車開來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.92,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼   我們東京見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的   請慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.43,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩周.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離我跟泉水結合那像夢境般的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經過了兩周了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因為外景拍攝無法抽身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一直都想跟泉水見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在終於能回東京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又可以跟泉水見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就回去！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿勒  有短信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.13,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍馬說他已經完成外景拍攝 正趕著回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  這不是挺好的嗎i
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊.....    嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是好事.....吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.92,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？  睡不著嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你沖杯熱可可吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲    我明天有什麼行程嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.10,0:07:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看      明天沒有安排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.64,0:08:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎   沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒    你為什麼這麼失望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為他們兩個進展得挺順利的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是吵架了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說   玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.62,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事要拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是難得的沒有行程的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是自從跟泉水確立關係後的第一次約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的約會計畫是完美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我會開車去接泉水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.61,0:08:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在Nanahongi Hills看電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來在Hiroio裡享用午餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著我們就去笠置水族館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.29,0:09:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在御台場上給泉水買衣服作為禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在可以看到美麗夜景的青坂的飯店裡用晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上是我們第二次的.....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好   就這麼上了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊   龍馬嗎   我現在就出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.85,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello~龍馬君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.39,0:10:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒   那個  為什麼你的家長們會在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊    哈哈哈  嚇一跳了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起   龍馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.03,0:10:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩人說怕會出什麼事所以硬要跟上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是.....是嗎..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.12,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒   啊  沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必介意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是跟你見面就已經很高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒    我們走吧   龍馬君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.55,0:10:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這車真不錯啊      拜託你當司機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.35,0:10:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹的    為什麼會是這樣的展開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍馬君      人家想去遊樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.73,0:10:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泉水和玲也想去的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯......嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來聽聽我的歌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Crusherz......誒？沒放進去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思   我的歌的話倒是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 Let's go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥煤的    給老子等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.83,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會跟泉水兩個人單獨相處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.43,0:11:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Iucky~比我想像中的還要少人啊   真是個好地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  那個人是聖湖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後面的不是龍馬嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.52,0:11:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是私人活動時間    請不要打擾我們哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的   我們知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.15,0:11:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私人時間請勿打擾   這應該是我的臺詞才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  龍馬    快來快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來合影吧   合影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲 幫我們拍照吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍馬君    一起來   起司~~
